Almost 50 branches will be closed in Gauteng alone, with 11 closing in the Western Cape. JOHANNESBURG - In March, Standard Bank made the shocking announcement that it would be closing down over 100 branches around the country, with many jobs to be lost as a result. The bank has now released a list of all the branches affected. Almost 50 branches will be closed in Gauteng alone, with 11 closing in the Western Cape. Here's the full list of branches: Standard Bank branches to be closed by Primedia Broadcasting on Scribd 